headline: Zimmer Biomet Announces CE Mark Certification for Persona速 Revision Knee System
summary: Zimmer Biomet Holdings, Inc. (NYSE: ZBH and SIX: ZBH), a global medical technology leader, today received the CE Mark for its Persona速 Revision Knee System. This addition to the Persona family builds on Zimmer Biomet's commitment to personalized solutions, providing surgeons with advanced tools for revision knee arthroplasty.
